title: Urbanization in Tanzania 2018
yAxis: Share of urban population in total population
summary: This statistic shows the degree of urbanization in cambodia from 2008 to 2018 . urbanization means the share of urban population in the total population of a country . In 2018 , 36.63 percent of cambodia 's total population lived in urban areas and cities .
gold: This statistic shows the degree of urbanization in Tanzania from 2008 to 2018 . Urbanization means the share of urban population in the total population of a country . In 2018 , 33.78 percent of Tanzania 's total population lived in urban areas and cities .
